doc.after: The most popular sports in Georgia are football basketball rugby union wrestling judo and weightlifting Historically Georgia has been famous for its physical education it is known that the Romans were fascinated with Georgians physical qualities after seeing the training techniques of ancient Iberia 195 Wrestling remains a historically important sport of Georgia and some historians think that the Greco Roman style of wrestling incorporates many Georgian elements 196
